Validation: it focus on the method
Validation: it is talking about product itself

First goal: To meet customer requirements
(It leads validation testing)
Second goal: To discover situation in which the behaviour of the software is incorret,undisreble or does
not conform to its specification
(It leads defect testing)

Inspection and testing:
Software Inspection: static analysis of the system
Software testing: Concerned with exercising and oberserving product behaviour(test data and its operational behaviour)

